Cyberpunk style: A sleek futuristic desktop videophone with a tilted LCD screen displaying static and glitching error patterns, sitting on a cluttered tech workstation bathed in harsh neon pink and electric blue lighting. The phone's camera lens glows an ominous red while fragmented digital artifacts scatter across the screen like broken glass. Tangled ethernet cables snake around the device, some unplugged and dangling. The background shows rain-streaked windows of a high-rise apartment with distant holographic billboards blurred in the night. The mood is frustration meeting failed technology—promising hardware defeated by incompatible systems. Reflective surfaces catch the neon glow, creating dramatic shadows and highlights across the abandoned-looking communication device.
